   22b2   68 ca 64 46       RLDI 10, SCORE_HI
   22b6   99                GHI 9               ; high byte → SCORE_HI (lower address)
   22b7   5a                STR 10
   22b8   1a                INC 10
   22b9   89                GLO 9               ; low byte → SCORE_LO (higher address)
   22ba   5a                STR 10
                        
