                            ; Different signs - positive number is greater
   2359   9d                GHI 13              ; score high byte
   235a   fa 80             ANI $80
   235c   ca 23 ce          LBNZ NEGAMAX_NO_BETA_CUTOFF  ; Score negative, beta positive: score < beta, NO cutoff
                            ; Score positive, beta negative: score > beta, CUTOFF (fall through)
                        
   235f                 NEGAMAX_DO_BETA_CUTOFF:
